-- Germany’s de Maiziere Seen by CDU as Wulff Successor, FAZ Says
-- B y   S h e e n a g h   M a t t h e w s
-- 2012-01-12T07:13:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-12/germany-s-de-maiziere-seen-by-cdu-as-wulff-successor-faz-says.html
Germany ’s  Christian Democratic Union 
is considering Defense Minister Thomas de Maiziere for the post
of German president in case Christian Wulff steps down,
 Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung reported , without saying where it
got the information.  De Maiziere, who has good relations with other political
parties, would be presented as a “common candidate,” backed by
the opposition as well as the government, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sheenagh Matthews in Frankfurt at 
 smatthews6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at 
 bkammel@bloomberg.net  